times.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴55-300x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴55-300x185.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴55.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">一品雪花牛</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652726\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴56-300x188.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"313\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴56-300x188.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴56-400x250.jpg 400w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴56.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">墨鱼籽花虾</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652727\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴57-300x195.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴57-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴57.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">鱼翅四宝</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652728\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴58-300x206.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴58-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴58.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">汤-清汤松茸</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652729\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴59-300x206.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴59-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴59.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">汤-菊花豆腐汤</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652730\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴60-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴60-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴60.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">汤-参皇养生汤</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652731\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴61-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴61-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴61.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">汤-黑菌芦笋汤</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652732\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴62-300x206.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴62-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴62.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">主菜-黄扒大排翅</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652733\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴63-300x206.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴63-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴63.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">主菜-鱼翅四宝</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-652734\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴64-300x206.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴64-300x206.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/08/国宴64.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: